# === Cau hinh reporter MAC + latency (metrics-report.ps1) ===
# Sao chep file nay thanh "metrics.conf" (CUNG thu muc) va dien TOKEN.
#
# TOKEN phai GIONG HET secret METRICS_TOKEN tren server (deployHeadscale).
# Neu de TOKEN trong -> reporter KHONG chay (khong gui gi).
#   Tao token (vd):  openssl rand -hex 32
#
# Khi co metrics.conf, start-tailscale.bat se tu chay reporter AN cung luc bat
# tailscale. Tat: xoa/doi ten metrics.conf.
TOKEN=
SERVER=https://vpn2.hangocthanh.io.vn
INTERVAL=60
PINGCOUNT=2
